OL,3,CAir passengers 'risking lives' by
OL,4,Ctaking baggage during evacuations
OL,6,FAir passengers are increasingly
OL,7,Fstopping to collect baggage or take
OL,8,Fphotos during aircraft evacuations,
OL,9,Fputting lives at risk, the
OL,10,FInternational Air Transport
OL,11,FAssociation has warned.
OL,13,FThe global airlines body launched the
OL,14,F'Save a Life, Not a Bag' campaign on
OL,15,FTuesday after it said a growing number
OL,16,Fof passengers haven't been following
OL,17,Fflight crew instructions during
OL,18,Femergencies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
