OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781032284
OL,3,CAir passengers 'risking lives' by
OL,4,Ctaking baggage during evacuations
OL,6,FAn IATA survey conducted on recent air
OL,7,Ftravellers from the UK, US, UAE and
OL,8,FSingapore found only 61% knew what to
OL,9,Fdo in an emergency evacuation.
OL,11,FOne in 10 people admitted they may
OL,12,Fstill take baggage during an
OL,13,Fevacuation, even when instructed not
OL,14,Fto.
OL,16,FThe IATA said valuable seconds can be
OL,17,Flost when retrieving baggage from
OL,18,Foverhead bins, and carrying bags can
OL,19,Fcause people to fall or block exits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
