OL,3,CAir passengers 'risking lives' by
OL,4,Ctaking baggage during evacuations
OL,6,FSome passengers have even been seen
OL,7,Fattempting to evacuate while carrying
OL,8,Fboth infants and bags or other
OL,9,Fpersonal items.
OL,11,FLast year, passengers on board a UK-
OL,12,Fbound Ryanair flight from Majorca's
OL,13,FPalma Airport were evacuated after a
OL,14,F"false alarm" during safety
OL,15,Fdemonstrations.
OL,17,FEighteen passengers were injured
OL,18,Fduring the evacuation, which one
OL,19,Fpassenger described to ITV News at the
OL,20,Ftime as "utter chaos".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
