OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781032284
OL,3,CAir passengers 'risking lives' by
OL,4,Ctaking baggage during evacuations
OL,6,FNick Careen, IATA's Senior Vice
OL,7,FPresident for Operations, Safety and
OL,8,FSecurity, warned there is a
OL,9,F"significant gap in knowledge" among
OL,10,Fsome travellers, that could result in
OL,11,Fdisaster.
OL,13,F"Even just a passenger or two taking a
OL,14,Ffew extra seconds to gather personal
OL,15,Fitems can endanger lives... it's
OL,16,Fimportant that passengers understand
OL,17,Fthe consequences of not listening to
OL,18,Fcrew," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
