OL,3,CAir passengers 'risking lives' by
OL,4,Ctaking baggage during evacuations
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCareen said it's important for
OL,12,Ftravellers to build good habits, "pay
OL,13,Fattention to safety demonstrations
OL,14,Fevery time and keep essential items,
OL,15,Fsuch as passport, money, and
OL,16,Fmedication on your person".
OL,18,FThe IATA says in the unlikely event of
OL,19,Fan emergency, passengers should:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
